<br>
It's a lot more enjoyable experience to dive in a week or two after launch.  Sure, I might not be the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>first</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to discover zone X or quest Y or Monster Z... but it's not as frustrating doing it.<br>
<br>
