<br>
Ultima Online is a good example... the game during beta was completely different then the one they launched with... they even changed a bunch of the graphics for the characters and monsters.  <br>
<br>
If I'd played UO during beta, I might not have ever bought the retail version... and yet the retail version, during it's first few months, was the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>most</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> fun I have ever had in an MMORPG to date.<br>
